Eloric Vilesilencer <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=madlokus>MadLokus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#333333>(11/6/02 7:40:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=398.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Let me clarify</span><hr size=1> I find that if i use the earth pet and get an add i can back my pet off the first mob (if root is sticking, it only needs to stick for maybe 5 seconds) and get him to attack the one thats on me.<br>
Spam the back off command then once hes off the first mob he will go straight for the second one thats been beatin on you. Once your pet gets argo on the second mob you can send him back onto the first one you were fighting. Kill the first one and then its easy pickings. <br>
