kegulik <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zyrexxshadowfyre@themagicianstower>Zyrexx Shadowfyre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 466<br> <font color=#333333>(11/7/02 6:59:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=398.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Let me clarify</span><hr size=1> Also Magicians don't run around in dirty animal skins, don't scratch themselves in public, take a bath more than once every ten years, dont have fleas and dont have a gas problem (though I think its the warder with the gas more often than the Lord) . *grin*<br>
<br>
Anyways the choice between the two classes realy is weather you like to mix it up face to face or stand back and throw in magical muscle. <p>Zyrexx Shadowfyre<br>
